data.description: What a view! One level home situated in a beautiful, quiet country setting with gorgeous mountain and farmland views. Spacious and move in ready with over 1200 sq ft of living space and an open floor plan. Many updates throughout including a new furnace and heat pump just replaced in May of 2023 and still under warranty, new bathroom fixtures, new stove, and more. The property offers a 12X24 shop with electricity and an attached carport. Relax on the covered front porch. Plenty of privacy and garden space!
